  "text": "By applying the Tor-spectral sequence in [CITATION_1] Proposition 7.7 ] to the commutative motivic ring spectrum Σ ∞ P ∞ + ∧ KGL and its modules KGL and Σ ∞ X τ + ∧ KGL we arrive at the strongly convergent tri-graded spectral sequence",
